        persons: ["Abraham Lincoln", "Jefferson Davis", "George McClellan", "Robert E. Lee", 'Thomas "Stonewall" Jackson', "Clara Barton", "Ulysses S. Grant", "William Tecumseh Sherman", "Robert Gould Shaw", "John Wilkes Booth"],
